==== Published Critique in Nature Communications

Davenport et al.\ published a formal commentary in _Nature Communications_ @effortcritique2025 stating that the effort preference interpretation “risks reinforcing skepticism about the serious biological nature of [ME] and its hallmark of post-exertional malaise (PEM), as well as its potential misclassification as a mental health condition.”

